data.description: Lovely 2 story in the highly sought after Fox Hollow neighborhood, with 4+1 Bedrooms and 4 Bathrooms! Here's the goods! Main level has formal living and dining, informal living/sitting room/office, powder bath, main level laundry, and an eat-in kitchen with plenty of cabinet / counter space (granite), and stainless steel appliances! Upstairs you'll find 3 guest bedrooms, a full bathroom, plus a huge primary suite that has 2 walk-in closets, dual vanity, jacuzzi tub, and a walk in shower! Downstairs is a large rec room, lots of storage space, a non-conforming bedroom (potential for egress window / 5th legal bedroom), and a 3/4 bathroom. Outside a large corner / cul-de-sac lot with beautiful landscaping, a privacy fenced yard, and outstanding curb appeal! If you're looking for a wonderful house in a prime location, that's very close to great schools, dining, and shopping.. well you know what to do!Now offering $5,000 towards buyer's closing costs / interest rate buy down!
